_fle    старт   1
*
* Floating-point relational Less or Equal:  result = (a <= b).
* Pop two FP values from stack (a at mem[r15-1], b in A).  Push raw 0/1 back.
*
* NTR (R := 0) selects full FP mode so the subtract normalizes and rounds.
* Before returning, each path restores R := 7 (the integer mode b/save leaves
* in place).  The NTR 7 must follow the branch, since NTR overwrites omega.
*
_true   внешн   ._true
        ржа
        вч      (15)            ; A := b - a (FP); additive sign set
        по      true            ; b - a >= 0  ->  a <= b
        сч
        ржа     7               ; restore integer mode for the caller
        пб      (13)
*
true    сч      _true           ; A := 1 (true)
        ржа     7               ; restore integer mode for the caller
        пб      (13)
        финиш
